metadata.name: DIN'S MAX PAIN
metadata.description: My first web3 art piece, the genesis. Wanted to do something experimental and fun. Decided to make a 3d sculpture with 2d elements inspired by my favourite piece MAX PAIN. This is not a collaboration but more of a homage to the legendary artist XCOPY. Would love to get the chance to collaborate one day. What a better way to start my journey here than paying respects to those who come before me.
